# ============================================
#  DRIVER APP API CONFIGURATION
# ============================================
# 
# This is the ONLY file you need to update when your IP changes!
# 
# HOW TO FIND YOUR IP:
# 1. Double-click "GET_IP.bat" in the root folder
#    OR
# 2. Open Command Prompt and run: ipconfig
# 3. Look for "IPv4 Address" (e.g., 192.168.0.155)
# 
# THEN UPDATE THIS LINE with your IP:
EXPO_PUBLIC_API_URL=http://192.168.0.155:5000/api
#
# EXAMPLES:
# Home WiFi:   http://192.168.1.100:5000/api
# Office WiFi: http://10.0.0.50:5000/api
# Hotspot:     http://192.168.43.1:5000/api
#
# After changing, restart the driver app (npm start)
# ============================================
